<p id="mw9A">with <span class="texhtml " about="#mwt134" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"math","href":"./Template:Math"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"&apos;&apos;H&apos;&apos;"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mw9Q"><i>H</i></span> the enthalpy defined by</p>

<dl id="mw9g"><dd id="mw9w"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt504" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"H=U+PV."}}' id="mw-A"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle H=U+PV.}">
