-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./James_Clerk_Maxwell" title="James Clerk Maxwell" id="mwAko">Maxwell, J.C.</a> (1871), p.v.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-43" id="cite_note-43"><a href="./Heat#cite_ref-43" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-43" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Peter_Atkins" title="Peter Atkins" id="mwAks">Atkins, P.</a>, de Paula, J. (1978/2010), p. 54.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-44" id="cite_note-44"><a href="./Heat#cite_ref-44" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-44" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Brian_Pippard" title="Brian Pippard" id="mwAkw">Pippard, A.B.</a> (1957/1966), p. 15.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-45" id="cite_note-45"><a href="./Heat#cite_ref-45" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-45" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./J.R._Partington" title="J.R. Partington" id="mwAk0" class="mw-redirect">Partington, J.R.</a> (1949), p. 118.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-46" id="cite_note-46"><a href="./Heat#cite_ref-46" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-46" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./James_Clerk_Maxwell" title="James Clerk Maxwell" id="mwAk4">Maxwell, J.C.</a> (1871), p. 10.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-47" id="cite_note-47"><a href="./Heat#cite_ref-47" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-47" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./James_Clerk_Maxwell" title="James Clerk Maxwell" id="mwAk8">Maxwell, J.C.</a> (1871), p. 11.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-48" id="cite_note-48"><a href="./Heat#cite_ref-48" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span><